      <h1 class="hero-big-title">
        Everything you need to know to get started with <span class="gradient-text">Freedom of Information</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="hero-subtitle">Freedom of Information <abbr title="Freedom of Information">(FOI)</abbr> gives everyone an incredible power — the power to uncover information from public authorities. </p>
      <p>Making a request isn’t complicated or difficult, but with the information you receive, you can have a huge impact. People have used FOI to show the need for changes, to bring hidden injustices into the open… and even to reveal corruption or malpractice. </p>
      <p>You might use FOI to find out facts within your own local area, or you might obtain stats across the whole of the UK. You could be following your own curiosity, or pursuing a wider societal benefit. Whatever is behind your need to know, FOI is a great tool for bringing information into the open, where everyone can access it.</p>
    </div>

